notes: Seti Astro Suite Pro V1.10.7 Bug Fixes V1.10.6 Temp stretch options in Cosmic Clarity UI. SPCC bug fixes for those running from the installer. Syqon Preview option during star removal. V1.10.5 SPCC, option to use GAIA fallback or not, introduces caching for synthetic photometry, fixes download error. GLMR bug fix. V1.10.4 Update to SPCC to add GAIA spectrum fallback to the simbad pickles spectrum. Update to Planetary Stacker for Planet derotation. Various other UX niceties.  V1.10.3 Fixed Remove Stars shortcut headless runner, added brightness slider to planetary stacker blink, added temp stretch amount parameter for syqon starless. V1.10.2  AxiomV2 Syqon Starless model support  V1.10.1 Added Franks Settings in Stacking Suite setting profiles, CLAHE blend option, Syqon addition to comet stacking, New blend options in layers, debayer offsets addition, utf-8 fixes. V1.10.0 Major update to Cosmic Clarity Sharpen and Denoise. Completely different neural net architecture. New AI4 models will need to be downloaded. There is a Lite Denoise model which may run faster for those with slower computers. Overall massive leap in Cosmic Clarity. Crop Dialog now has center crosshair. Numerous other updates and improvements throughout.
